   "source": [
    "# NEU NeuralOS — Dynamic Routing Training\n",
    "\n",
    "Trains NeuModel with **dynamic per-token routing** between:\n",
    "- **SSM (Mamba-2)** — global context, sequential\n",
    "- **Local Attention** — hard retrieval, windowed\n",
    "- **Cheap MLP** — ~2x FLOPs of embedding, no attention\n",
    "\n",
    "Key innovations vs baselines:\n",
    "- Learned per-token router (vs fixed interleaving in Fixed Hybrid)\n",
    "- Persistent state across blocks (GRU on sequence summary)\n",
    "- Load-balancing loss (prevents router collapse to one path)\n",
    "- Temperature annealing (soft training → hard routing at inference)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Runtime**: T4 GPU (~16GB) | **Training**: ~6-8 hours | **Scale**: 150M params"
   ]
  },
